---
// ServicesSection.astro - Sección de Servicios
---

<section id="services" class="py-24 bg-gray-50/50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <!-- Pequeño detalle visual hexagonal antes del título -->
      <div class="mb-6 relative flex justify-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full">
            <polygon points="50 0, 93.3 25, 93.3 75, 50 100, 6.7 75, 6.7 25" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" class="opacity-60"></polygon>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight mb-4">
        Nuestros <span class="font-medium">servicios</span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-black/60 font-light leading-relaxed">
        Soluciones digitales personalizadas que combinan diseño impactante con funcionalidad intuitiva para impulsar tu presencia online.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
      <!-- Servicio 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-black/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/5 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-black/5 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-black" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
