            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-3">Diseño Web</h3>
        <p class="text-black/60 mb-6">Creamos sitios web modernos, responsivos y optimizados que cautivan a los visitantes y reflejan la identidad de tu marca.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-black/60 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-black mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            Diseño UX/UI centrado en el usuario
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-black mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            Sitios web adaptativos para todos los dispositivos
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-black mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            Optimización para motores de búsqueda (SEO)
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services#web-design" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium">
          <span>Conocer más</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Servicio 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-black/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/5 hover:-translate-y-1">
